title: George Jones - 50 Television & Live Performances 1958-1988
description:
This is a collection of 50 George Jones performances on video, mostly taken from TV appearances in the sixties and seventies. I've been collecting these for years and decided to it was time to share them with the other George Jones fans out there. As far as I know none of these have been released commercially. They're very hard to track down on sites like Youtube because they're buried under thousands of crappy  videos of Jones studio songs set to slideshows, etc. None of that here - this is all genuine footage of him singing his heart out on national television.

The greatest country singer of all time - May he rest in peace! 

Video quality varies from excellent to fair. 

Load magnet link to view track listing.

Enjoy!
